    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即预约，享有限量优惠！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 特典迷你游戏《双截龙躲避球》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 24小时早鸟优惠（豪华版限定）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※《双截龙躲避球》是与游戏正片分开的应用程序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【豪华版内容】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●双截龙再临</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●数位画廊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●数位原声带</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●新增角色颜色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※《双截龙再临》另有出售普通版。请注意重复购买。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※「数位画廊」和「数位原声带」是与游戏正片分开的应用程序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【游戏介绍】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1987年在电子游乐场内出现的&quot;横向捲轴动作&quot;的杰出之作《双截龙》系列，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至今仍带给众多玩家感动的作品，以《双截龙再临》再次重生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/3c84dd5365b657c454ef6cc1ba3519be.poster.avif?t=1761614101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/3c84dd5365b657c454ef6cc1ba3519be.webm?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/3c84dd5365b657c454ef6cc1ba3519be.mp4?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. 独具风格、焕然一新的角色视觉效果</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用3D图像技术再现了街机黄金时代的人物个性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅有主角李氏兄弟，历代与之对抗的强敌们也一起登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/a8e74abc8df177a041bac6e6a691a9c7.poster.avif?t=1761614101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/a8e74abc8df177a041bac6e6a691a9c7.webm?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/a8e74abc8df177a041bac6e6a691a9c7.mp4?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. 追求更彻底的&quot;横向捲轴动作&quot;的快感</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是玩家透过在画面中左右移动来打倒敌人的横向捲轴动作游戏，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忠实再现简洁又直观的游戏体验的同时，也将操作感与难度根据现代技术进行最优化，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经由亚克系统格斗游戏开发人员精心监製，即使是首次接触的玩家也能轻鬆游玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/67f7db3949c3ec6c76738f56fdb6a122.poster.avif?t=1761614101\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/67f7db3949c3ec6c76738f56fdb6a122.webm?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012220/extras/67f7db3949c3ec6c76738f56fdb6a122.mp4?t=1761614101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3. 动作感爽快且具战略性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的战斗动作并不是单纯按压按钮，而是更加丰富多样的操作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中包括记住敌人的行动模式，看准更有效的攻击时机等战略要素，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用掉落在各场景内的武器或准备好的陷阱，将战斗引导至更有利的方向吧！</p>",
